Employee_Name_FormOfAddress_Translation is a Form
    Layout
        paragraph
            Base_BusinessClass.Employee
                display as text
        single column
            IsoLocale
                compact format
                raise yellow alert when (VerifyTranslations_Name_FormOfAddress)
                    mouse over text is untranslatable:"The base data has been changed but this translation has not been verified"
        single column
            blank line
            header4 of untranslatable:"Translations for {0}"
            Base_BusinessClass.Name.FormOfAddress
                label is untranslatable:"Form Of Address"
            Name.FormOfAddress
                label is untranslatable:"Translated"
